title: Person of Interest - Bar Fight
author: Devalorize
comment: just seems like any bar fight is incomplete without some guy crashing through a window
"Hey Wall Street, you lost?", I laugh everytime to the manner in which it was spoken
When I first saw this part: I remember grinning and saying "Pfft, Amateurs. You got nothing on Reese."
It would have been hilarious if Reese followed the guy he threw out the door by breaking his way through the remaining glass (instead of taking the other door).
Always the gentleman when he talks and able to teach others manners. Such eloquence can not be bought! One must be born with it!!!
description: Mr. Reese takes care of business, as usual.
